<h3 id="_unlocking_a_pos_user">4.5. Unlocking a POS user</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If an incorrect password is entered several times in succession, the login will be blocked for the user for a certain time. As a user with admin rights, you can unlock the user manually in the plentymarkets back end.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Unlocking a user:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
