<p>Go to <strong>Settings » Basic settings » User » Accounts » Open user</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Unblock login</strong>.<br>
→ The user will be able to log into the plentymarkets App.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
