<div class="paragraph">
<p>For POS orders to be processed in plentymarkets correctly, you need to allow the shipping method <strong>Self pickup</strong> for those items you want to bill through plentymarkets POS. The following preparations are necessary:</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The following preparations are necessary to allow POS users access to plentymarkets POS:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Creating a shipping service provider for <strong>pickup</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Creating a shipping profile <strong>Pickup</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Activating a shipping profile for an item</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
