<h3 id="240">12.2. Unlinking a POS from a device</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can unlink a POS from a device. Instead, either link a different POS to the device or select no POS.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Unlinking a POS from a device:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Open the plentymarkets App.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>plentymarkets App » Settings » POS beta</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>For the setting <strong>POS</strong>, select a different POS or the empty option.</p>
</li>
<li>
